For HRadmin, the numbers in front shows the process flow.
They are there for the ease of debugging :)

1. Course (Create or Manage course)

2. Create course
    2.1 New Course (Fill in description)
    2.2 Trainer List (Assign a Trainer to the Course)
    2.3 Updated New Course (Hardcoded updated assigned trainer)

3. Manage course
    3.1 Course List
    3.2 Class list (Shows enrolled)
    3.3 Enrol Learner (Shows learners)
    3.4 Updated Class List (Hardcoded updated enrolled learners)